[14/03/2017 01:07:16] <font color="#ffffff">Bueno...</font>
[14/03/2017 01:07:19] <font color="#ffffff">-No, por favor.</font>
[14/03/2017 01:07:19] <font color="#ffffff">(R EN)</font>
